Z","msg":"尋晚都有提到少少沙拿同費明奴中鋒支點輪換問題，比巴打笑我八奇思考，依家拎出來同大家討論下<br />\n<br />\n高普係將正前鋒支點位定位為「半休息位」。全場跑動唔多，令球員可以「半休息」，尋晚費明奴又拉邊，又墮後回防，非常消耗體力，但對般尼茅夫同拿坡里個場就打正中鋒做支點，叫做有稍稍休息到。反而個兩場沙拿就搏到盡，仲表現得好好。今場對獌就比沙拿企「半休息位」回下氣，費明奴就大爆發。沙拿/費明奴輪樓企「半休息位」，雖然都會消耗體力，但都可以話係一個唔錯嘅輪換，兩位球員一人爆一場，都叫做運籌帷握，呢個奇特輪換方法值得留意同讚賞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"何蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f09718f97e4bd20f304ebafe4e8531cef714e69","tid":944252,"uid":59931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要砌futmas f9 我要用埋隻25圖先夠86 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊交唔交"},{"pid":"0de4ef5f2068db9369053cf04b3cd7bdcf913c41","tid":944252,"uid":11655,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"唔使再開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下個post講番狼隊仲好我覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc22384f7336134b254508e0b39be2067e06c6d9","tid":944252,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f09718f97e4bd20f304ebafe4e8531cef714e69","tid":944252,"uid":59931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要砌futmas f9 我要用埋隻25圖先夠86 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊交唔交"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"好後悔做左flashback 丹狗，閘根本唔使咁勁"},{"pid":"f25b7ff213fa0e2d673ea347fea9710a4ebb13fa","tid":944252,"uid":151982,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0de4ef5f2068db9369053cf04b3cd7bdcf913c41","tid":944252,"uid":11655,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"唔使再開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下個post講番狼隊仲好我覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\